        "gg3BajX3jAe_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">I absolutely love that <strong>refreshing</strong>, <strong>cooling feeling</strong>... especially after a day in the sun—it’s one of my favorite parts of my routine. <strong>Our mask gives you that calming, spa-like effect</strong>, even when you're just relaxing at home. It soothes, hydrates, and calms any heat or redness, leaving your skin with a gorgeous, radiant glow—such a simple, luxurious way to unwind and take care of yourself! <strong>If you haven’t tried it yet, you're in for a treat!</strong></span></p>",
        "gg5jhvAeOg-_text": "<p>Try It for 60 Days, Totally Risk-Free</p>",
