        "ggL99cbnlZo_text": "<p>GUARANTEED: In just a couple of hours, the Nifora facial mask makes your skin glow so brightly you won’t believe your mirror. If you think you've surpassed Korean beauty standards with just one application, you’re right. This is what Nifora can do for you every time you use it.</p>",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p>By Molly Richards<br>Last Updated Jule, 24 2025</p>",
        "ggN-h1PmvDV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/For_LP_9.png",
        "ggNzvrSfCrV_text": "2. Scientifically Proven Ingredients",
        "ggOGc25WEdF_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Here’s the exciting part—you’re in luck! We’ve got a <strong>limited-time offer</strong> just for you. I’m sure you’ll love the <strong>Bio-Collagen Mask</strong>, but if not, you will get a refund, no questions asked. It is<strong> 60-day risk free,</strong> so why not give it a try? You deserve glowing skin!</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggOkzpODfF8_text": "6.&nbsp;Cooling &amp; Soothing Effect",
        "ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">When I hear a product is a celebrity favorite, I have to try it—and once I tried our mask, I totally got why it’s so loved. It’s not just about the natural ingredients, but the <strong>amazing results</strong>. People are obsessed with how it gives them that flawless, youthful glow, and the best part? It’s <strong>all natural!</strong> If it’s good enough for them, it’s definitely good enough for us!</span></p>",
        "ggQPtwZzMvG_text": "4. Sensitive Skin Friendly",
        "ggTCZJLSmNN_text": "7. Exclusive Summer Sale is now Live!",
        "ggUMmUh3HgV_label": "<p>Shop Now</p>",
        "ggUYRw8nmHu_text": "Discover why 40,000+ women switched to our affordable Collagen Gel Mask to Repair Sun Damage and Restore Youthful, Glowing Skin.",
        "ggUrpHf4v9e_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">As we get older and <strong>endure daily UV exposure</strong>, our skin definitely needs more recovery. I’ve noticed <strong>my skin craves extra hydration</strong> to stay plump and glowing, and that’s where collagen comes in. Especially in its low-molecular-weight form (sounds fancy, but it works wonders!), it goes deep into your skin to keep it hydrated and refreshed all day. Trust me, <strong>it keeps my skin hydrated and refreshed all day</strong>, reversing that dry, leathery feeling from the sun!</span></p>",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-ead342dd-6162-44aa-9cec-ffd056a84b84.webp",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-ead342dd-6162-44aa-9cec-ffd056a84b84.webp",
