        "ggvDN5djePx_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Who says repairing sun-damaged skin has to be expensive? <strong>The right products can transform your skin without breaking the bank!</strong> Healthy, radiant skin doesn't have to cost a fortune!</span></p>",
        "ggw6GWQLv30_text": "<p>1 - 2 applications a week - instant results</p>",
